  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA10">
<l>irunālva rīraintiṉ mēloruva reṭṭō</l>
<l>ṭorunālva rōriruva rallāl tirumāṟ</l>
<l>kiyāmār vaṇakkamā rēpāva naṉṉeñcē</l>
<l>nāmā mikavuṭaiyō nāḻ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Except for the twice Four, the One above the twice five,</l>
<l>the once Four with eight, the once Two, for Tirumāl</l>
<l>who are we? Obeisance to whom, hey, alas, good heart?</l>
<l>We, ah, possess much fault.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
